    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1936-03-03T23:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1936-03-03T23:00:00-05:00" n="757"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d757">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">894.00/595: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Grew</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tokyo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-03-04T13:00:00+09:00"
                            >March 4, 1936—1 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received March 4—1 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>57. Department’s 28, March 3, 5 p.m. The Embassy is now compiling a despatch
                    containing all available official announcements, official radio broadcasts,
                    leaflets, et cetera, which will be transmitted in the pouch due Washington March
                        21.<note n="30" xml:id="d757fn30">Despatch No. 1721, March 6, not
                        printed.</note> It is improbable, however, that all the official details
                    desired by the Department will be available for some time to come owing to
                    continued censorship and the fact that even the officials of the Foreign Office
                    are not yet certain of all the details. The whole subject will be fully covered
                    in due course.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
